# Weekly Order Monitoring & Reporting Workflow

An automated n8n workflow that fetches order data from an ERP system on a weekly basis, filters orders by status and assigned employee, registers matching orders in Airtable, and sends a summary report to a Discord channel.

---

## Overview

| Property       | Detail                          |
|----------------|---------------------------------|
| **Platform**   | n8n                             |
| **Trigger**    | Scheduled — Every Monday at 9:00 AM |
| **Status**     | Inactive (template / manual activation required) |
| **Integrations** | ERP (HTTP), Airtable, Discord |

---

